            "purpose": "提取幂等写入：内置 pydantic 校验（ExtractionV3）、冲突检测→raise、thread_updates 落图、consumption_balance 复算。取代现有 write_extraction。",
            "signature": "python -m src.novel_kg.mcp_cli apply_extraction --project <proj> --chapter <N> [--json-file PATH]"
