        "schema_or_mechanism": "### 1. 文件布局（src/novel_kg/ 新增）\n```\nsrc/novel_kg/\n├── constraint_engine/             # 新增包\n│   ├── __init__.py\n│   ├── rules.yaml                 # 声明式约束规则（单一真相源，可版本化）\n│   ├── contracts.py               # pydantic schema（ExtractionV3 / ArcV3 / AgentReturnV3）\n│   ├── validators_v3.py           # 纯计算函数（无 IO）：grep 复算 / consumption_balance 复算 / 代词扫描\n│   ├── gates.py                   # 守门函数（enforce_*_gate）：组合 validators，返回 Decision\n│   ├── finalizer.py               # integrity_reconcile：跨文件对账\n│   └── repair_prompt.py           # 定向改写 prompt 生成器\n├── validators.py                  # 保留兼容（旧版调用转发到 v3）\n└── mcp_cli.py                     # 注册新命令\n```\n\n### 2. 声明式规则 rules.yaml\n```yaml\nversion: 3\nconstraints:\n  style_notXisY:\n    kind: style_grep\n    pattern: '不是.*?[，。].*?是'\n    per_k_thresholds: {green: 1.5, yellow: 2.5, red: 3.0}    # 每千字\n    absolute_max: 5                                              # 绝对上限（防短章节博弈）\n    aggregation: sum\n  style_dashes:\n    kind: style_grep\n    pattern: '——'\n    per_k_thresholds: {green: 2.0, yellow: 3.0, red: 3.5}\n    absolute_max: 18\n  style_periods:\n    kind: style_grep\n    pattern: '[。]'\n    per_k_thresholds: {green: 18, yellow: 15, red: 12, ceiling: 25}\n    direction: floor_and_ceiling                                # 句号密度双向\n  word_count:\n    kind: numeric\n    thresholds: {green_min: 3000, yellow_min: 2800, red_min: 2500, ceiling: 5000}\n  pronoun_gender:\n    kind: semantic_map\n    source: world_setup.json#characters[gender]\n    scan: '(他|她|它|祂)'\n    mismatch_is: red\n  suspense_consumption:\n    kind: derived\n    formula: 'sum(resolved*1.0 + advanced*0.5 + partially_resolved*0.5 + abandoned*0.3)'\n    per_chapter_min: 0     # consumption_balance = consumed - planted >= 0\n    per_volume_floor_mature_drop: 'floor(N/3)'    # 卷级\n    per_volume_min_pruning: 10\n    per_volume_max_net: 0\n  chapter_arc_completeness:\n    kind: schema\n    required_fields: [purpose, scenes, ending, structure_type]\n    min_scenes: 2\n    scenes_non_empty: true\n  event_chapter_field:\n    kind: schema\n    required: true\n    on_missing: raise        # 不再是 stats.notes\n  outline_compliance:\n    kind: programmatic_then_semantic\n    bigram_overlap_min: 2\n    pending_semantic_to: llm\ncross_chapter:\n  consecutive_yellow_to_red: 3\n  volume_integrity_mandatory: true\nrepair:\n  max_loops: 3\n  loop_fail_escalation: human\n```\n\n### 3. pydantic 契约（contracts.py）— 解决 RC2 字段漂移\n```python\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel, Field, validator, root_validator\nfrom typing import Literal, List, Optional\n\nclass EventV3(BaseModel):\n    id: str\n    title: str = Field(min_length=2)\n    detail: str = \"\"\n    chapter: int                                # 必填，缺失即 reject\n    event_type: str = \"scene\"\n    is_gap: bool = False\n\nclass ThreadUpdateV3(BaseModel):\n    \"\"\"统一字段名映射：agent 可能写 action/new_status 任一种，schema 层归一\"\"\"\n    thread_id: str\n    # 接受 action (prompt 文档版) 或 new_status (graph 内部版)，归一为 new_status\n    new_status: Literal[\"planted\",\"advanced\",\"partially_resolved\",\"resolved\",\"abandoned\"]\n    note: str = \"\"\n\n    @root_validator(pre=True)\n    def _merge_action_alias(cls, v):\n        if \"action\" in v and \"new_status\" not in v:\n            v[\"new_status\"] = v.pop(\"action\")\n        return v\n\nclass ExtractionV3(BaseModel):\n    \"\"\"所有 agent 写入的提取 JSON 必过此 schema\"\"\"\n    events: List[EventV3] = Field(min_items=1)\n    thread_updates: List[ThreadUpdateV3] = []\n    new_threads: List[dict] = []\n    new_characters: List[dict] = []\n    new_locations: List[dict] = []\n    # 不接受 self-report 数值字段（如 threads_consumed, consumption_balance）\n    # 如果 agent 写了，pydantic 默认忽略（extra='ignore'）\n    class Config:\n        extra = 'ignore'\n\nclass ArcV3(BaseModel):\n    chapter: int\n    purpose: str = Field(min_length=10)\n    scenes: str = Field(min_length=20)\n    ending: str = Field(min_length=5)\n    structure_type: Literal[\"linear\",\"intercut\",\"flashback\",\"parallel\"] = \"linear\"\n\nclass AgentReturnV3(BaseModel):\n    \"\"\"ChapterAgent 返回主编排的结构 — 仅 status/IDs/issues，禁止数值质量字段\"\"\"\n    status: Literal[\"ok\",\"partial\",\"failed\"]\n    chapter: int\n    title: str\n    issues: List[str] = []\n    # 显式拒绝：threads_consumed / consumption_balance / grep_after 等\n    # （pydantic 用 extra='forbid' 让 agent 偷塞数值字段时直接 reject）\n    class Config:\n        extra = 'forbid'\n```\n\n### 4. 守门函数（gates.py）— 解决 RC1+RC4\n```python\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\nfrom enum import Enum\nfrom typing import List\n\nclass Tier(str, Enum):\n    GREEN = \"green\"        # pass\n    YELLOW = \"yellow\"      # pass but log；连续3次升级 red\n    RED = \"red\"            # trigger repair_loop\n    CRITICAL = \"critical\"  # block dispatch / kill volume\n\n@dataclass\nclass Violation:\n    rule_id: str\n    tier: Tier\n    computed_value: float          # 机器复算值（不是 agent 自报）\n    threshold: float\n    location: str                  # 段落/行号定位\n    directional_fix_prompt: str    # 直接喂给改写 agent 的定向 prompt\n\n@dataclass\nclass Decision:\n    tier: Tier\n    violations: List[Violation]\n    next_action: str               # \"pass\" | \"repair_style\" | \"repair_extract\" | \"block_dispatch\" | \"prune_volume\"\n\ndef enforce_style_gate(project, chapter) -> Decision:\n    \"\"\"复算所有 grep 类指标，按 rules.yaml 阈值分级\"\"\"\n    text = _read_final_text(project, chapter)        # 直接读盘，不信 agent 传入\n    cn_count = _count_chinese_chars(text)\n    violations = []\n    for rule_id, rule in RULES['constraints'].items():\n        if rule['kind'] != 'style_grep': continue\n        matches = re.findall(rule['pattern'], text)\n        per_k = len(matches) / (cn_count / 1000)\n        abs_count = len(matches)\n        # 双重门禁：per_k 和 absolute_max 任一超即违规\n        if per_k > rule['per_k_thresholds']['red'] or abs_count > rule['absolute_max']:\n            violations.append(Violation(\n                rule_id=rule_id, tier=Tier.RED,\n                computed_value=per_k, threshold=rule['per_k_thresholds']['red'],\n                location=_locate_violations(text, rule['pattern'], matches[:3]),\n                directional_fix_prompt=_build_fix_prompt(rule_id, matches, location)\n            ))\n    tier = max((v.tier for v in violations), default=Tier.GREEN)\n    return Decision(tier=tier, violations=violations,\n                    next_action=\"pass\" if tier == Tier.GREEN else \"repair_style\")\n\ndef enforce_suspense_quota(project, chapter) -> Decision:\n    \"\"\"每章消费/播种平衡 + 卷级累计强制收敛\"\"\"\n    kg = _kg(project)\n    # 从 graph.json 复算（不信 extraction JSON 的 self-report）\n    chapter_updates = kg.get_thread_updates_for_chapter(chapter)\n    consumed = sum(1 for u in chapter_updates if u.new_status == \"resolved\")\n    consumed += sum(0.5 for u in chapter_updates if u.new_status in (\"advanced\",\"partially_resolved\",\"abandoned\"))\n    planted = len(kg.get_threads_planted_at(chapter))\n    balance = consumed - planted\n    if balance < 0:\n        return Decision(tier=Tier.RED, violations=[...],\n                        next_action=\"repair_extract\")\n    # 卷级聚合\n    vol_start, vol_end = _get_volume_range(project, chapter)\n    vol_mature_drop = _compute_mature_drop(project, vol_start, vol_end)\n    if vol_mature_drop < RULES['suspense_consumption']['per_volume_floor_mature_drop'](vol_end-vol_start+1):\n        return Decision(tier=Tier.CRITICAL, violations=[...],\n                        next_action=\"prune_volume\")\n    return Decision(tier=Tier.GREEN, ...)\n\ndef enforce_chapter_completeness(project, chapter) -> Decision:\n    \"\"\"章间硬门禁：替换 verify_chapter_complete。返回 tier 驱动 workflow\"\"\"\n    decisions = [\n        enforce_style_gate(project, chapter),\n        enforce_length_gate(project, chapter),\n        enforce_pronoun_gate(project, chapter),         # 新增：代词-性别映射\n        enforce_arc_completeness(project, chapter),     # ArcV3 schema\n        enforce_event_chapter_field(project, chapter),  # raise on missing\n        enforce_outline_compliance(project, chapter),\n        enforce_integrity(project, chapter),            # 多文件对账\n    ]\n    worst = max((d.tier for d in decisions), default=Tier.GREEN)\n    return Decision(tier=worst, violations=sum([d.violations for d in decisions], []),\n                    next_action=_action_for_tier(worst))\n```\n\n### 5. 修复回路（repair_prompt.py + workflow 钩子）— 解决 B1+B2\n```python\ndef directional_rewrite_prompt(violation: Violation, full_text: str) -> str:\n    \"\"\"定向改写：只让 agent 改违规段落，不动其他部分（防 B2）\"\"\"\n    target_paras = _paras_containing(violation.location, full_text)\n    return f\"\"\"【约束修复任务】\n检测到违规：{violation.rule_id}（实测 {violation.computed_value:.2f}，阈值 {violation.threshold}）\n仅修改以下段落（不得改动其他段落）：\n{target_paras}\n要求：\n1. 删除/重写上述段落中的违规句式\n2. 不得引入新的「不是X是Y」、破折号、内心独白\n3. 不得压缩剧情（保持段落数与字数）\n4. 输出完整章节（不是片段）\n\"\"\"\n```\nWorkflow JS 端（编排层）：\n```js\n// volume-pipeline-v3.js（修订）\nconst decision = run(`mcp_cli enforce_chapter_completeness --project ${project} --chapter ${ch}`)\nif (decision.tier === 'GREEN') dispatch(ch+1)\nelse if (decision.tier === 'RED') {\n  for (let i = 0; i < 3; i++) {\n    run_agent_with_prompt(decision.violations[0].directional_fix_prompt)\n    const recheck = run(`mcp_cli enforce_chapter_completeness ...`)\n    if (recheck.tier === 'GREEN') break\n    if (recheck.new_violations > decision.violations.length) {\n      // B2 检测：新违规数增加 → 升级到 CRITICAL\n      escalate_to_human(ch)\n      break\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 6. 整卷最终对账 finalizer — 解决 RC5\n```python\ndef integrity_reconcile(project, volume=None) -> Decision:\n    \"\"\"卷结束必跑：对账 6 个真相源\"\"\"\n    mismatches = []\n    chapters = _range_for_volume(project, volume) or _all_chapters(project)\n    for ch in chapters:\n        # 1. output/*.txt 存在？\n        # 2. extraction JSON 与 graph events[chapter==ch] 数量一致？\n        # 3. chapter_arcs[ch] 存在且 ArcV3 校验通过？\n        # 4. digests/ch{NN}.json 存在？\n        # 5. world_setup.total_chapters == max(chapters)？\n        # 6. events 中 chapter 字段全部 == ch？\n        ...\n    # 缺失项：digests 自动 generate_context_digest 补；arcs 触发 raise\n    return Decision(tier=Tier.CRITICAL if mismatches else Tier.GREEN,\n                    violations=mismatches,\n                    next_action=\"block_volume_close\" if mismatches else \"pass\")\n```\n\n### 7. 三级阈值统一抽象（含碎片组）\n每个 rule 有 4 档：GREEN（自动通过）→ YELLOW（log + 计入\"连续3章\"）→ RED（修复回路）→ CRITICAL（强制 prune / 阻断卷收尾）。\"碎片组\"概念：每章 5 个 YELLOW 不报警但当章一个 RED 即阻断；连续 3 章 YELLOW 升级为 RED（防\"每章都刚好不红\"博弈）。\n\n### 8. CLI 命令注册（mcp_cli.py）\n新增命令（旧命令保留兼容，内部转发）：\n- `enforce_chapter_completeness --project --chapter [--max-loops N]` — 替换 verify_chapter_complete\n- `enforce_style_gate --project --chapter` — 单独跑风格门禁（debug 用）\n- `enforce_suspense_quota --project --chapter` — 单独跑悬链门禁\n- `repair_loop --project --chapter --gate style|extract|graph` — 触发修复回路\n- `validate_extraction_v3 --project --chapter --json-file PATH` — pydantic 校验（reject 即 raise）\n- `integrity_reconcile --project [--volume V]` — 卷级/全书对账",
        "subsystem": "constraint-engine（约束引擎子系统 v3）— 把 grep/字数/代词/悬链消费/arc 完整性等所有质量约束，统一变成代码层硬门禁，agent 自报字段一律不进判定路径"
      },
      {
        "core_principles": [
          "P1 单一真相源（SSOT）：所有质量数值字段（consumed/balance/grep 阈值/threads_consumed/periods_per_k）必须由 Python CLI 从最终正文 + graph.json 重算，agent 写入的同名字段在 schema 层标 `x-advisory: true`，校验器自动剥离，绝不进入 verify/telemetry/review 的判定路径",
          "P2 写入即校验（validate-on-write）：所有 add_*/write_* 函数必须先过 pydantic schema，不通过 raise ValueError 而非返回 dict；detect_* 的输出必须以 raise 形式驱动 gatekeeper 阻断，禁止 'detect to notes'",
          "P3 字段契约固化在 schema：所有 agent 产出的 JSON 用 pydantic BaseModel 定义；字段别名（action ↔ new_status）、公式（consumed = resolved×1 + (advanced+partial+abandoned)×0.5）、枚举值（status 状态机）在 import 时一次性映射，代码与 prompt 不允许各说各话",
          "P4 提取幂等（idempotent extraction）：write_extraction 必须能基于最终正文 + 现有图谱完全重算 thread_updates 的图谱影响，不依赖 agent 是否调用了 update_suspense_thread；agent 只产出声明，CLI 负责落图",
          "P5 跨卷状态版本化（vol-snapshot）：角色性别/代词、设定常数、时间线锚点从 handoff.md 提取为结构化 schema（CharacterIdentitySnapshot），按 vol 快照存储，每章 boot context 注入对应 vol 的硬约束块",
          "P6 悬链状态机强约束：planted→developing→mature→{resolved|advanced|abandoned} 的合法迁移图固化在 SuspenseThread model，非法迁移直接 raise；mature 下降/pruning 配额作为 dispatch_ch{N+1} 前的硬门禁",
          "P7 完整性机器对账（integrity reconcile）：每卷结束运行 integrity_reconcile(project, vol)，对账 extractions/digests/arcs/events-chapter-field/world_setup 一致性，缺失项自动补齐或 raise，取代 'verify_chapter_complete 后相信全书完整'",
          "P8 可重算 grep 基准：所有风格 grep（notXisY/dash/period）的实现版本固化在 validators.py（同 regex、同字符集 [一-鿿]、同千字除法），agent prompt 中 grep 命令视为文档示例；validate_chapter 用代码版重算并覆盖 agent 自报"
        ],
        "failsafe": "LLM 可能的绕过路径与本子系统的兜底：(1) **填假数字**——agent 在 telemetry JSON 写 consumption_balance=4 但实际只回收 1 条。兜底：telemetry schema 标记所有数值字段 x-advisory=true，enforce_telemetry_consistency() 强制从 graph.json 重算覆盖，agent 写的值仅存档于 raw_agent_advisory 块不进判定。(2) **字段名漂移**——agent 写 action='resolved'，期望绕过 new_status 检查。兜底：pydantic alias 映射在 import 入口固化，agent 写什么都映射到规范名；映射失败（unknown 字段）pydantic 默认 ignore，但 chapter_arc/event 等核心实体用 extra='forbid' 拒绝未知字段，迫 agent 看错误信息修正。(3) **空字段绕过**——agent 写 scenes='' 空字符串让必填检查 'if not scenes' 触发但实际填了空串。兜底：pydantic 用 min_length=1 + StripWhitespace validator，空串/纯空白在 schema 层 reject。(4) **伪造 chapter 字段**——agent 给所有 event 填 chapter=180 但实际章节是 181。兜底：EventChapterValueValidator 强制 event.chapter == path-derived chapter，从 extraction_ch{NN}.json 文件名反推 NN，agent 写错直接 raise。(5) **代词绕过**——agent 用 '其'/'彼' 等古汉语代词避开 '她/他' 扫描表。兜底：pronoun_lexicon 是可扩展 deny-list，validate_chapter 全文扫描时若发现未被 lexicon 收录但疑似代词的字（基于 NLP 词性标注或启发式：'X+动作' 中 X 是单字且重复出现），触发 review_required 标记人工审核。(6) **状态机绕过**——agent 把一条 planted 线直接标 resolved 跳过 developing/mature。兜底：SuspenseStateMachine.transition() 拒绝 planted→resolved 直接迁移（除非 importance=high 且有 evidence_link），raise IllegalStateTransition。(7) **跨卷快照绕过**——agent 跳过 vol 快照直接写 character.gender。兜底：update_character() 检测 gender/pronouns 字段变更时强制要求 vol_snapshot 存在，否则 raise MissingSnapshotError。(8) **detector 静默绕过**——agent 调 detect_conflicts 后忽略返回的 errors。兜底：detect_conflicts 不再返回 list，改为 yield Issue 对象，Issue.severity=high 的必须在调用方 catch 后 raise；CLI 层 detect_* 函数增加 raise_on_error=True 默认参数。(9) **JSON 半截写入**——agent 写 extraction JSON 中途崩溃留下半个文件。兜底：所有写入走 atomic_write（temp file + os.replace），不完整文件不会出现；schema 校验在 atomic_write 之前，校验失败文件根本不落盘。(10) **直接编辑 graph.json 绕过 CLI**——agent 用文件编辑工具改 graph.json。兜底：每次 _kg(project) 加载时跑 schema_reconcile_on_load()，发现非法字段/缺失 vol_snapshot/integrity 指标退化则 raise LoadRefusedError，迫使走 CLI 修复。(11) **agent 自创公式**——agent 用 consumed=resolved×2 改公式。兜底：consumed 的计算只在 cli/suspense_ledger.py 一处定义，agent 看到的 prompt 公式是文档；telemetry 重算时调用 ledger.recompute_consumed() 而非读 agent 自报。(12) **agent 提前 return 跳过 Telemetry 步**——兜底：verify_chapter_complete 增加第 6 项 telemetry_check（ch{N}_report.json 必含 word_count/grep_metrics/thread_ledger 三个机器重算字段），缺失即 complete:false，dispatch ChN+1 被拦截。",
        "interfaces": "与【CLI 守门子系统】接口：(1) detect_conflicts / verify_chapter_complete / verify_pipeline_step 的返回值从 dict 改为 raise，守门子系统负责 catch 后决定 retry/abort；(2) 提供 schema_validator.validate(payload, kind) 给守门层在 add_event/add_chapter_arc/write_extraction 前调用；(3) suspense_ledger.recompute_consumed() / get_volume_quota_status() 给守门层做 dispatch_chN+1 前的硬门禁判定。与【编排子系统】接口：(1) workflow.js 在 Phase 边界（章间/卷末）调用 verify_chapter_complete / integrity_reconcile，返回 raise 时由编排决定回滚/重试；(2) 提供 get_boot_context_vol_snapshot(project, chapter) 注入角色性别/代词到 boot prompt 的硬约束块；(3) 提供 VolumeIntegrityReport 给编排判断是否进入 VolumeReview。与【Prompt 子系统】接口：(1) prompt 模板从 schema 自动生成字段说明（schema_to_prompt_doc()），消除 prompt 与代码的字段漂移；(2) prompt 中所有 'should/建议/if X then Y' 文字由 schema 约束 + 守门代码双重镜像，prompt 只承担 '用法说明'；(3) 提供 advisory_only 字段列表给 prompt 子系统，让其在 prompt 中明确标注 '以下字段 agent 填写仅供参考，最终值由 CLI 重算'。与【回读校验子系统】接口：(1) VolumeReviewAgent 调用 reconcile.reconcile_volume(project, vol) 拿到 Issue 列表（已过滤 advisory-only）；(2) 提供 cross_chapter_consistency_check()（人物状态连续性 / 时间线单调性 / 悬链状态机合法性）给 VolumeReview 做跨章维度。",
        "key_apis": [
