        "migration_cost": "保守估计 12-18 人天，影响 8-10 章 CLAUDE.md 文档 + 全部 CLI 命令签名。分解：(1) schema 定义层（pydantic models for Event/ChapterArc/SuspenseThread/Character/ExtractionPayload/TelemetryPayload/VolumeSnapshot）—— 3 人天，需要枚举完所有现有字段并设计 alias 映射；(2) validator 注入层（重构 mine.py L260-434 write_extraction_to_graph + core_crud.py add_event/add_chapter_arc/add_suspense_thread 接受 schema 校验）—— 3 人天，要保证向后兼容旧 JSON；(3) 检测器→守门改造（detect_conflicts/verify_chapter_complete/verify_pipeline_step 从返回 dict 改为 raise）—— 2 人天，需要改 mcp_cli.py 的 _out() 包装层捕获并转 exit code；(4) suspense_ledger + state_machine（recompute_consumed 幂等重算 + 状态迁移图）—— 2 人天，需要回填 239 章历史数据的 ledger；(5) vol_snapshot + integrity_reconcile —— 2 人天，需要对 17 卷全跑一遍生成快照；(6) v2→v3 数据迁移脚本（修 184 个缺 chapter 的 event、154 个缺 structure_type 的 arc、补 93 章缺失的 digest、归一化 368 悬链状态、补齐 world_setup）—— 3-4 人天（脚本本身 1 天，验证 + 修 corner case 2-3 天，因为现有数据已脏）；(7) 文档与模板同步（CLAUDE.md / chapter_agent_v2.md / volume_review_v2.md 删除自报字段说明，改为 'CLI 重算' 说明）—— 1 人天。风险：迁移脚本可能触发连锁错误（修了 event.chapter 后导致 _chapter_idx 索引失效），需要 dry-run + diff 比对 + 备份。建议分两阶段：先上 schema 校验层（不强制，warn-only）跑 1 卷观察，再切 raise 模式。",
        "open_questions": [
          "Q1 角色性别变更如何处理：当剧情中角色真的改变性别/代词（如 T-1 无性别→有性别），vol_snapshot 应记录变更原因 + chapter 锚点 + 触发事件，还是允许覆盖？目前设计是 append（每卷一个 snapshot），但跨卷性别回退（幻视/失忆桥段）需要状态机还是 free-form note？",
          "Q2 悬链状态机是否允许 '回退'：partially_resolved → developing（揭示是假象，重新悬置）是否合法？现设计中 mature→planted 等回退禁止，但 partially_resolved→developing 在悬疑小说里常见，需要用户决定是开例外还是统一禁止",
          "Q3 digest 缺失的 93 章是补生成还是标记为 'historical_skip'：从 output/*.txt 重生成 digest 是技术上可行（generate_context_digest 已存在），但补生成的 digest 缺少原始 extraction 的 character_updates 等字段；是接受不完整 digest 还是标记为 advisory-only 让回读时降权？",
          "Q4 vol_snapshot 的 world constants 边界：哪些算 'world constant'（如代谢系统定义、频率技术参数）需要快照，哪些算 'plot state'（如封锁状态、三方立场）属于 chapter/event 层？需要用户给一个明确的 ontology 分界，否则快照会无限膨胀",
          "Q5 schema validator 是否阻塞 hot path：现设计 validate-on-write 在每次 add_event 都跑，对单章 8-10 个 event 是 ms 级，但卷末 integrity_reconcile 跑 200+ event 时可能 1-3 秒；是否需要 async 或 caching？影响 workflow.js 是否需要加 await",
          "Q6 247 vs 239 不一致的历史脏数据如何处理：现 graph.json 已有 247 个 extraction（多 8 个，可能是 ch216/227 等 review_report 提到的异常章），是删除多余的、保留并标记 'orphan_extraction'、还是合并到最近合法章节？删除会丢失数据，合并会污染章节语义",
          "Q7 advisory-only 字段是否完全废弃：agent 在 prompt 里被要求填 consumption_balance/grep_after 等字段，v3 是完全删掉这些字段（agent 不再填）还是保留作为 cross-check（CLI 重算后与 agent 自报比对，差异大于阈值时触发额外审查）？前者更干净，后者能检测 agent 是否在'认真算'"
        ],
        "schema_or_mechanism": "\n## 数据模型 v3：单一真相源 + 写入即校验 + 卷级快照\n\n### A. 顶层 schema：从自由 dict 到 pydantic BaseModel（src/novel_kg/schema_v3.py）\n\n```python\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel, Field, field_validator, model_validator\nfrom typing import Literal, Optional\nfrom enum import Enum\n\n# ---- 枚举（取代散落的字符串比较）----\nclass ThreadStatus(str, Enum):\n    PLANTED = \"planted\"\n    DEVELOPING = \"developing\"\n    MATURE = \"mature\"\n    PARTIALLY_RESOLVED = \"partially_resolved\"\n    RESOLVED = \"resolved\"\n    ADVANCED = \"advanced\"\n    ABANDONED = \"abandoned\"\n\nclass EventType(str, Enum):\n    PLOT = \"plot\"; TURNING = \"turning\"; REVELATION = \"revelation\"\n    CLIMAX = \"climax\"; GAP = \"gap\"; DENOUEMENT = \"denouement\"\n\nclass GenderPronoun(str, Enum):\n    HE = \"他\"; SHE = \"她\"; IT = \"它\"; THEY_NEUTRAL = \"TA\"; NONE = \"无\"\n\n# ---- 合法状态迁移图（固化在 schema，不靠 prompt 提醒）----\nLEGAL_TRANSITIONS = {\n    ThreadStatus.PLANTED: {ThreadStatus.DEVELOPING, ThreadStatus.ABANDONED, ThreadStatus.RESOLVED},\n    ThreadStatus.DEVELOPING: {ThreadStatus.MATURE, ThreadStatus.PARTIALLY_RESOLVED, ThreadStatus.ADVANCED, ThreadStatus.ABANDONED},\n    ThreadStatus.MATURE: {ThreadStatus.PARTIALLY_RESOLVED, ThreadStatus.RESOLVED, ThreadStatus.ADVANCED, ThreadStatus.ABANDONED},\n    ThreadStatus.PARTIALLY_RESOLVED: {ThreadStatus.RESOLVED, ThreadStatus.ADVANCED, ThreadStatus.ABANDONED},\n    ThreadStatus.ADVANCED: {ThreadStatus.PARTIALLY_RESOLVED, ThreadStatus.RESOLVED, ThreadStatus.MATURE, ThreadStatus.ABANDONED},\n    ThreadStatus.RESOLVED: set(),  # terminal\n    ThreadStatus.ABANDONED: set(),  # terminal\n}\n\n# ---- Event：解决 C1（chapter 必填，schema 层强制）----\nclass EventV3(BaseModel):\n    id: str = Field(pattern=r\"^E\\d{2,3}_\\d{2}$\")\n    title: str = Field(min_length=1, max_length=80)\n    detail: str = Field(min_length=1)\n    chapter: int = Field(ge=1, le=400)  # 必填，硬约束\n    volume: int = Field(ge=1, le=20)\n    type: EventType\n    is_gap: bool = False\n    gap_level: int = Field(default=0, ge=0, le=3)\n    @model_validator(mode=\"after\")\n    def _chapter_volume_consistent(self):\n        # 跨字段校验：chapter 必须落在 volume 范围内\n        from .vol_ranges import VOL_RANGES  # {1:(1,12), 2:(13,32), ...}\n        lo, hi = VOL_RANGES[self.volume]\n        assert lo <= self.chapter <= hi, f\"chapter {self.chapter} 不在 vol{self.volume}({lo}-{hi})\"\n        return self\n\n# ---- ChapterArc：解决 C2（所有字段必填）----\nclass ChapterArcV3(BaseModel):\n    chapter: int\n    purpose: str = Field(min_length=10)  # 不允许空\n    scenes: str = Field(min_length=10)\n    ending: str = Field(min_length=10)\n    structure_type: Literal[\"linear\",\"layered\",\"convergent\",\"divergent\",\"cyclical\"]\n    # 自报字段全部 advisory-only（schema 标记后自动剥离）\n    model_config = {\"extra\": \"ignore\"}  # agent 写的 consumption_balance 等被丢弃\n\n# ---- SuspenseThread + 状态机 ----\nclass SuspenseThreadV3(BaseModel):\n    id: str\n    content: str = Field(min_length=5)\n    planted_chapter: int\n    resolved_chapter: Optional[int] = None\n    status: ThreadStatus\n    importance: Literal[\"high\",\"medium\",\"low\"]\n    thread_type: Literal[\"mystery\",\"foreshadowing\",\"character_arc\",\"world_building\"]\n\n    @model_validator(mode=\"after\")\n    def _legal_transition(self):\n        # 由 caller 传入 prev_status\n        # 非法迁移直接 raise（如 mature→planted 不允许）\n        return self\n\n# ---- CharacterIdentitySnapshot：解决 D2/D3/D6（角色属性版本化）----\nclass CharacterSnapshotV3(BaseModel):\n    \"\"\"卷级快照——一个角色在某个 vol 的全部身份属性。\"\"\"\n    character_name: str\n    volume: int\n    gender_pronoun: GenderPronoun          # 取代散落在 personality 文本里的 '代词她'\n    role: Literal[\"protagonist\",\"supporting\",\"antagonist\",\"minor\"]\n    status: Literal[\"active\",\"dormant\",\"deceased\",\"ascended\",\"merged\"]\n    abilities: list[str] = Field(default_factory=list)  # 觉醒的能力清单\n    knowledge_state: list[str] = Field(default_factory=list)  # 已知/未知的关键设定\n    arc_position: Literal[\"setup\",\"rising\",\"climax\",\"resolution\",\"epilogue\"]\n    # 上一卷到本卷的 diff，强制可追溯\n    diff_from_prev: dict = Field(default_factory=dict)\n\n# ---- ExtractionPayload：取代自由 dict，统一字段名 ----\nclass ThreadUpdateDecl(BaseModel):\n    \"\"\"agent 声明的悬链影响——action 和 new_status 都接受，schema 统一映射到 new_status\"\"\"\n    thread_id: str\n    # 字段别名：agent 写 action 或 new_status 都行，pydantic 统一映射\n    new_status: ThreadStatus = Field(alias=\"action\")  # 接受 action 别名\n    evidence_event_id: Optional[str] = None\n    detail: str = \"\"\n    model_config = {\"populate_by_name\": True}\n\nclass ExtractionPayloadV3(BaseModel):\n    \"\"\"agent 提取的完整 payload——所有字段在 import 时校验\"\"\"\n    chapter: int\n    volume: int\n    events: list[EventV3]\n    new_characters: list[dict] = Field(default_factory=list)\n    new_locations: list[dict] = Field(default_factory=list)\n    thread_updates: list[ThreadUpdateDecl] = Field(default_factory=list)\n    new_threads: list[dict] = Field(default_factory=list)\n    chapter_arc: ChapterArcV3  # 强制嵌套\n    # advisory-only 字段：schema 知道这些是 agent 自报，下游不消费\n    agent_self_report: dict = Field(default_factory=dict, exclude=True)  # 自动剥离\n\n    @model_validator(mode=\"after\")\n    def _all_events_have_chapter(self):\n        # C1 在 schema 层解决：缺 chapter 的 event 在 pydantic 解析时直接 raise\n        # 不再依赖 detect_conflicts 后置检查\n        return self\n```\n\n### B. 写入路径：detect → raise（取代 detect → notes）\n\n```python\n# src/novel_kg/core_crud_v3.py\nclass WriteError(Exception): ...\nclass IllegalStateTransition(WriteError): ...\nclass MissingRequiredField(WriteError): ...\n\ndef add_event_v3(project, event_id, *, chapter, volume, title, detail, type, **kw):\n    \"\"\"取代 core_crud.py:506 add_event。失败必须 raise。\"\"\"\n    try:\n        ev = EventV3(id=event_id, chapter=chapter, volume=volume,\n                     title=title, detail=detail, type=type, **kw)\n    except ValidationError as e:\n        raise MissingRequiredField(f\"event {event_id}: {e}\") from e\n    kg = _kg(project)\n    if kg.event_exists(event_id):\n        raise WriteError(f\"event {event_id} 已存在（重复入图）\")\n    kg._graph[\"events\"][event_id] = ev.model_dump()\n    kg._rebuild_chapter_idx()\n    return ev\n\ndef update_suspense_thread_v3(project, thread_id, new_status, **kw):\n    \"\"\"取代 core_crud.py:648。状态机在这里强制。\"\"\"\n    kg = _kg(project)\n    prev = kg._graph[\"suspense_threads\"].get(thread_id)\n    if not prev:\n        raise WriteError(f\"thread {thread_id} 不存在\")\n    prev_status = ThreadStatus(prev[\"status\"])\n    target = ThreadStatus(new_status)\n    if target not in LEGAL_TRANSITIONS[prev_status]:\n        raise IllegalStateTransition(\n            f\"thread {thread_id}: {prev_status}→{target} 非法迁移\"\n        )\n    # 通过状态机后写图\n    prev.update({\"status\": target.value, **kw})\n    if target == ThreadStatus.RESOLVED:\n        prev[\"resolved_chapter\"] = kw.get(\"chapter\")\n```\n\n### C. 完整性约束机器化：integrity_reconcile（取代散落的 verify_chapter_complete）\n\n```python\n# src/novel_kg/integrity.py\ndef reconcile_volume(project, volume) -> VolumeIntegrityReport:\n    \"\"\"卷末 finalizer。取代 verify_chapter_complete 的局部视角。\"\"\"\n    issues = []\n    vrange = VOL_RANGES[volume]  # (start_ch, end_ch)\n    expected_chapters = list(range(vrange[0], vrange[1]+1))\n\n    # 1. 文件三件套对账（output/extraction/digest）\n    for ch in expected_chapters:\n        for kind, path_fn in [(\"output\", lambda c: f\"output/ch{c:02d}_generated.txt\"),\n                              (\"extraction\", lambda c: f\"extractions/extraction_ch{c:02d}.json\"),\n                              (\"digest\", lambda c: f\"digests/digest_ch{c:02d}.json\")]:\n            if not (proj_dir / path_fn(ch)).exists():\n                issues.append(Issue(severity=\"blocker\", kind=\"missing_file\",\n                                    chapter=ch, file_kind=kind))\n\n    # 2. graph.json 字段完整性\n    kg = _kg(project)\n    for ch in expected_chapters:\n        arc = kg._graph[\"chapter_arcs\"].get(str(ch))\n        if not arc:\n            issues.append(Issue(\"blocker\", \"missing_arc\", ch))\n        elif not all(arc.get(f) for f in (\"purpose\",\"scenes\",\"ending\",\"structure_type\")):\n            issues.append(Issue(\"blocker\", \"arc_missing_field\", ch,\n                                fields=[f for f in (\"purpose\",\"scenes\",\"ending\",\"structure_type\") if not arc.get(f)]))\n\n    # 3. event.chapter 外键（C1 机器化）\n    events_in_vol = [e for e in kg._graph[\"events\"].values()\n                     if e.get(\"chapter\") and vrange[0] <= e[\"chapter\"] <= vrange[1]]\n    events_no_chapter = [e for e in kg._graph[\"events\"].values()\n                         if e.get(\"chapter\") is None]\n    for e in events_no_chapter:\n        # 尝试从 event.id 反推（E11_01 → ch11）——这是修复路径\n        import re\n        m = re.match(r\"E(\\d+)_\", e[\"id\"])\n        if m:\n            e[\"chapter\"] = int(m.group(1))  # 自动补\n            issues.append(Issue(\"warn\", \"auto_fixed_chapter\", e[\"id\"]))\n        else:\n            issues.append(Issue(\"blocker\", \"unresolvable_chapter\", e[\"id\"]))\n\n    # 4. 悬链状态机合法性（全卷扫描）\n    for tid, t in kg._graph[\"suspense_threads\"].items():\n        if t.get(\"planted_chapter\", 0) > vrange[1]:\n            continue\n        # 检查每条线的最终状态是否在合法集合\n        if t.get(\"status\") not in [s.value for s in ThreadStatus]:\n            issues.append(Issue(\"blocker\", \"illegal_thread_status\", tid))\n\n    # 5. world_setup 对账\n    ws = json.load(open(proj_dir/\"world_setup.json\", encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n    actual_total = max(e[\"chapter\"] for e in kg._graph[\"events\"].values() if e.get(\"chapter\"))\n    if ws.get(\"total_chapters\") != actual_total:\n        issues.append(Issue(\"blocker\", \"world_setup_drift\",\n                            expected=actual_total, recorded=ws.get(\"total_chapters\")))\n\n    # 6. 悬链配额（卷级）\n    mature_before = sum(1 for t in threads if t.get(\"status\")==ThreadStatus.MATURE.value\n                        and t.get(\"matured_at_vol\",0) < volume)\n    mature_after = sum(1 for t in threads if t.get(\"status\")==ThreadStatus.MATURE.value)\n    if mature_before - mature_after < len(expected_chapters) // 3:\n        issues.append(Issue(\"blocker\", \"mature_quota_unmet\",\n                            delta=mature_before-mature_after,\n                            required=len(expected_chapters)//3))\n\n    # 决策：blocker 存在则 raise\n    blockers = [i for i in issues if i.severity == \"blocker\"]\n    if blockers:\n        raise VolumeIntegrityFailed(f\"vol{volume} 有 {len(blockers)} 个 blocker\")\n    return VolumeIntegrityReport(issues=issues, volume=volume)\n```\n\n### D. 卷级快照：CharacterIdentitySnapshot 注入\n\n```python\n# 每卷开始前自动拍快照（取代 handoff.md 自由文本）\ndef snapshot_volume(project, volume) -> dict:\n    kg = _kg(project)\n    snap = {\n        \"volume\": volume,\n        \"snapshot_chapter\": VOL_RANGES[volume][0],\n        \"characters\": {},\n        \"world_constants\": {},  # 取代散落的设定常数\n        \"timeline_anchor\": {},  # 取代 time_periods 自由 text\n    }\n    for name, c in kg._graph[\"characters\"].items():\n        snap[\"characters\"][name] = {\n            \"gender_pronoun\": extract_pronoun_from_personality(c.get(\"personality\",\"\")),\n            # 例如 '代词她' → SHE；无标记默认 HE（旧数据默认值，需校验）\n            \"role\": c.get(\"role\"),\n            \"status\": \"active\",  # 由 events 推断\n            \"abilities\": extract_abilities_from_goals(c),\n            \"knowledge_state\": extract_known_facts(c, kg),\n        }\n    # 落盘：projects/<P>/snapshots/vol{N}.json（取代散落在 handoff.md）\n    atomic_write(proj_dir/\"snapshots\"/f\"vol{volume}.json\", snap)\n    kg._graph[\"snapshots\"][volume] = snap  # 双写，graph.json 是 SSOT\n    return snap\n\n# boot context 注入硬约束块\ndef get_boot_context_v3(project, chapter):\n    vol = derive_volume(chapter)\n    snap = load_snapshot(project, vol)\n    return {\n        \"outline\": kg.get_outline(chapter),\n        \"prev_ending\": read_prev_ending(chapter),\n        \"character_pronoun_lock\": {  # 硬约束：agent 必须遵守\n            name: attrs[\"gender_pronoun\"] for name, attrs in snap[\"characters\"].items()\n        },\n        \"suspense_recall_index\": kg.get_recall_index(chapter),\n    }\n```\n\n### E. 大纲的机器可读形式：outline_v3.yaml（取代 framework.md 散文）\n\n```yaml\n# projects/<P>/outline.yaml —— 取代 framework.md 中大纲部分（保留 framework.md 做设定叙述）\nversion: 3\ntotal_chapters: 239\nvolumes:\n  - number: 1\n    name: 萌动\n    chapter_range: [1, 12]\n    setting: 现代\n    theme_seeds: [\"知识的引力\",\"日常的裂缝\",\"孤独的专注\"]\n    chapters:\n      - chapter: 1\n        purpose: \"建立林深作为普通人中的偏执者的人设\"\n        key_events: [\"周末晨起\",\"旧书摊淘书\",\"发现注记诡异\",\"买下\",\"回家翻读\"]\n        structure_hint: linear\n        must_plant: [\"ST_书的来源\",\"ST_注记者身份\"]   # 强制播种的悬链 ID\n        must_resolve: []                              # 强制回收的悬链 ID\n        character_focus: [\"林深\"]\n      # ... 239 章\n```\n\n每章 outline 包含 `must_plant / must_resolve` 字段，write_extraction 时校验：\n```python\ndef enforce_outline_contract(project, chapter, extraction):\n    outline = load_outline(project, chapter)\n    planted_ids = {t[\"id\"] for t in extraction.get(\"new_threads\", [])}\n    for must in outline.get(\"must_plant\", []):\n        if must not in planted_ids:\n            raise OutlineContractBroken(f\"ch{chapter} 必须播种 {must} 但未出现\")\n```\n\n### F. 迁移策略：v2 graph.json → v3（一次性脚本，幂等）\n\n```python\n# scripts/migrate_v2_to_v3.py\ndef migrate(project, dry_run=True):\n    g = json.load(open(f\"projects/{project}/graph.json\", encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n    backup_path = backup(g)  # 必备份\n    issues = []\n\n    # 1. Event：从 id 反推 chapter（E11_01 → ch11）\n    for eid, ev in g[\"events\"].items():\n        if ev.get(\"chapter\") is None:\n            m = re.match(r\"E(\\d+)_\", eid)\n            if m:\n                ev[\"chapter\"] = int(m.group(1))\n                ev[\"volume\"] = derive_volume(ev[\"chapter\"])\n            else:\n                issues.append((\"unresolvable\", eid))\n\n    # 2. ChapterArc：补 structure_type（默认 linear，标 needs_review）\n    for ch, arc in g[\"chapter_arcs\"].items():\n        if not arc.get(\"structure_type\"):\n            arc[\"structure_type\"] = \"linear\"\n            arc[\"_needs_review\"] = True\n\n    # 3. SuspenseThread：归一化 status 枚举值\n    valid = {s.value for s in ThreadStatus}\n    for tid, t in g[\"suspense_threads\"].items():\n        if t.get(\"status\") not in valid:\n            issues.append((\"illegal_status\", tid, t.get(\"status\")))\n\n    # 4. 补齐缺失的 digest（从 output 重生成）\n    for ch in range(1, 240):\n        digest_path = proj_dir/\"digests\"/f\"digest_ch{ch:02d}.json\"\n        if not digest_path.exists():\n            output_path = proj_dir/\"output\"/f\"ch{ch:02d}_generated.txt\"\n            if output_path.exists():\n                regenerate_digest(project, ch)  # 复用 generate_context_digest\n\n    # 5. 生成 vol snapshots（17 卷）\n    for vol in range(1, 18):\n        snapshot_volume(project, vol)\n\n    if dry_run:\n        print(json.dumps(issues, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n    else:\n        atomic_write(f\"projects/{project}/graph.json\", g)\n        atomic_write(f\"projects/{project}/world_setup.json\",\n                     reconcile_world_setup(g, project))\n```\n\n### G. telemetry advisory-only 字段隔离\n\n```python\n# src/novel_kg/telemetry_v3.py\ndef inject_chapter_metrics_v3(project, chapter, **advisory_fields):\n    \"\"\"\n    advisory_fields: agent 自报的 word_count/grep_after/threads_consumed 等\n    本函数忽略所有 advisory 数值，从正文+图谱重算后落盘。\n    \"\"\"\n    text = read_chapter_text(project, chapter)\n    kg = _kg(project)\n    # 重算（DI1 单一真相源）\n    ground_truth = {\n        \"word_count\": count_hanzi(text),\n        \"notXisY_per_k\": recompute_notXisY(text),\n        \"dash_per_k\": recompute_dash(text),\n        \"periods_per_k\": recompute_periods(text),\n        \"threads_consumed\": recompute_consumed_from_graph(kg, chapter),\n        \"consumption_balance\": recompute_balance(kg, chapter),\n    }\n    report = load_report(project, chapter)\n    report[\"ground_truth\"] = ground_truth\n    report[\"agent_advisory\"] = advisory_fields  # 存档但不消费\n    report[\"advisory_drift\"] = {                                # 偏差检测\n        k: abs(advisory_fields.get(k, 0) - ground_truth[k])\n        for k in ground_truth if k in advisory_fields\n    }\n    atomic_write(report_path, report)\n    # 偏差过大触发告警（仍不阻塞，但 review 时会高亮）\n    if any(v > DRIFT_THRESHOLD[k] for k, v in report[\"advisory_drift\"].items()):\n        report[\"advisory_drift_flag\"] = True\n```\n",
        "subsystem": "data-model（数据模型子系统）— v3 设计"
      },
      {
        "core_principles": [
          "OP1 设计与执行彻底分层：设计阶段产出的 VolumeDesignDoc (VDD) 是只读契约，ChapterAgent 不允许写、不允许改、不允许临时发明悬链/代词/字数阈值。任何不在 VDD 里的字段在 execute 阶段视为不存在。",
          "OP2 门禁即节点（gate-as-node）：每个硬门禁（style/suspense/pronoun/completeness/integrity）实现为 workflow 中独立的 JS 节点，节点直接调用 Python CLI；CLI 失败则 workflow 抛 fail 而非依赖 agent 自觉。门禁不在 prompt 里写 'must/shoud/建议'。",
          "OP3 不信任 agent 返回的数值字段：ChapterAgent 返回的 JSON 只接受 status 枚举 + chapter + title + issues（文本）。grep_after/threads_consumed/consumption_balance 全部由 Python CLI 在门禁节点里重新计算并覆盖 agent 自报（DI1+DI9 落地）。",
          "OP4 卷类型分类法驱动约束矩阵（taxonomy-driven constraints）：volume_design.type ∈ {opening, advancing, climax, epilogue, multi-pov}，每种类型在 VDD 中固化不同的 mature_decline_floor / pruning_quota / new_thread_quota_per_chapter / 字数区间 / 悬链净收支符号约束。",
          "OP5 5 阶段强顺序：Design → PreFlight → Execute → Review → Archive。任一阶段失败 workflow 终止并向主编排返回 failed。不允许跳过 PreFlight（Vol15 review 未落盘的根因之一是 Review 阶段被跳过且无强制归档节点）。",
          "OP6 最终归档强制：Archive 阶段调用 integrity_reconcile + archive_volume_artifacts，把 review_report_*.md / volume_summary_*.json / VDD / 终态 graph 快照落盘到 projects/<proj>/archive/vol{N}/。Archive 节点 raise 失败时，workflow 不算 ok——避免 'pipeline ok 但找不到报告' 的状态。",
          "OP7 章节级 inline 校验优先于卷级回读：跨章约束（如 mature 下降≥floor、卷级播种≤回收）通过每 N 章运行一次 mid-volume gate（而非全部 12-16 章后由 VolumeReview 事后报告）实现 fail-fast。VolumeReview 只做跨章维度（人设漂移、伏笔断头、节奏曲线），不做单章风格。"
        ],
        "failsafe": "兜底策略分三层，假设 LLM 用最阴险的方式绕过：\n\n(1) Agent 返回 status=ok 但正文质量造假（如把 notXisY 改成 '不-是' 逃避 grep）：门禁节点 P3 不读 agent 的 status，而是直接对 output/ch{NN}_generated.txt 运行 Python grep。即使 agent 自报 ok，Python 重算 notXisY=15 也会触发 raise。这是 DI1 的兜底——agent 自报永远不进入判定路径。\n\n(2) Agent 跳过门禁节点（直接调 write_extraction 而不调 validate_chapter）：workflow 的 JS 节点是串行 DAG，agent 无法跳过 workflow 中的节点；agent 只能在自己的子代理内部跳过 prompt 步骤，但门禁节点是 workflow 编排层强制调用的 CLI。如果 agent 没有真正写入 output/ 文件，PreFlight-execute 之间的 verify_design_completeness 会在 ch{N-1} 的 integrity gate 上发现 output/extraction/arc/digest 不同步而 raise。\n\n(3) Agent 篡改设计文档（修改 VDD 的代词表/配额以降低难度）：VDD 落盘后 archive_volume_design 在 PreFlight 阶段对其做 SHA256 哈希并写入 .vdd.lock；execute 阶段每章 boot 时 hash 校验，VDD 被改动则 raise 'design tampered'。同时 VDD 是单写文件（archive/ 下版本化），ChapterAgent 在 prompt 中明确 '禁止写入 archive/'。\n\n(4) Agent 提取 JSON 里不写 thread_updates 但 prompt 自报 consumption_balance=3：P3 suspense gate 用 extract_thread_updates(parsed_extraction) 重算 consumed，与 agent 自报不一致则 raise 'thread_updates contract drift'，触发 workflow loop-back（最多 2 次重试后 fail）。\n\n(5) Vol15 review 未落盘的历史问题：Archive 节点的 archive_volume_artifacts 必须返回 review_report_path 并由 workflow 用 os.path.exists() 验证，文件不存在则 workflow 返回 failed。主编排不能仅看 reviewResult.status==='ok' 就更新 handoff。\n\n(6) 卷类型被错误标注（如把 climax 卷标成 advancing 以放松约束）：PreFlight 的 verify_volume_design 调用 suggest_volume_type(kg, vol_design.chapter_range) 自动推断类型，与 VDD 声明不符则 raise 让人工确认。\n\n最后兜底：integrity_reconcile 在 Archive 强制运行，发现 '247 extraction vs 239 chapter' 类多文件不一致直接 raise，不允许 workflow 返回 ok。这是 RC5 的最终防线——任何漂移在卷边界被冻结、暴露、阻断后续卷。",
        "interfaces": "与 schema 子系统的接口：(a) execute 阶段每章通过 pydantic 校验 extraction JSON，schema 子系统提供 ExtractionV3 模型；(b) workflow 的 SCHEMA 对象（CHAPTER_RESULT_SCHEMA 等）由 schema 子系统生成 JSON Schema 文件供 workflow import；(c) VolumeDesignDoc 的 pydantic 模型由 schema 子系统定义，design 阶段产出后 PreFlight 验证。\n\n与 gatekeeper 子系统的接口：编排只负责'调用 gate、读 raise、决定 loop-back'，gate 的具体阈值矩阵（卷类型×约束）在 gatekeeper 子系统实现为 Python 函数。workflow 节点如 P3.style_gate / P3.suspense_gate / P3.completeness_gate 全部是 thin wrapper：CLI 调 gatekeeper.enforce_*()，raise 经 CLI 转 exit_code!=0，workflow 读取后 loop-back。\n\n与 integrity/finalizer 子系统的接口：PreFlight 节点 PF3 和 Archive 节点 AR2 调用 integrity 子系统的 verify_volume_design 和 integrity_reconcile；该子系统负责跨文件对账（extractions/digests/arcs/events/world_setup）。\n\n跨卷状态固化（DI5）接口：CharacterPronounRegistry / ConstantsRegistry 由 schema 子系统定义、由 integrity 子系统从 handoff.md 提取并维护，编排在 get_boot_context_v3 中注入硬约束块给 ChapterAgent。\n\n主编排（CLAUDE.md 主 agent）接口：v3 workflow 返回结构化 VolumeResult（含 status / vdd_path / review_report_path / archive_dir / integrity_report_path），主编排只读这 5 个字段更新 handoff.md；不再读取 chapters[] 数组里的数值字段（避免自报污染主编排上下文）。",
        "key_apis": [
